      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;Last updated in June 2024&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;hello-i-am-an-assistant-professor-in-the-department-of-economics-at-the-hong-kong-university-of-science-and-technology-hkust&#34;&gt;Hello! I am an Assistant Professor in the Department of Economics at the Hong Kong University of Science and Technology (HKUST).&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;my-research-interests-are-environmental-economics-and-urban-economics&#34;&gt;My research interests are environmental economics and urban economics.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;subi-am-seeking-ideal-candidates-with-a-keen-interest-in-economics-and-sustainability-along-with-strong-analytical-skills-preference-will-be-given-to-students-who-are-proficient-in-stata-arcgis-r-andor-python-if-you-are-interested-please-email-your-cv-code-sample-and-a-writing-sample-to-dyraousthk-sponsorship-for-hong-kong-working-visa-is-available-sub&#34;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I am seeking ideal candidates with a keen interest in economics and sustainability, along with strong analytical skills. Preference will be given to students who are proficient in Stata, ArcGIS, R, and/or Python. If you are interested, please email your CV, code sample, and a writing sample to 
&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:dyrao@ust.hk&#34;&gt;dyrao@ust.hk&lt;/a&gt;. Sponsorship for Hong Kong working visa is available. &lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
